1. Basic Structure Tags
<!DOCTYPE html>   → Declares the document type (HTML5)
<html>            → Root of the document
<head>            → Metadata, title, links, etc.
<body>            → Visible content of the webpage

2. Text Formatting Tags
<h1> to <h6>      → Headings (h1 is biggest)
<p>               → Paragraph
<b>, <strong>     → Bold text (strong is semantic)
<i>, <em>         → Italic text (em is semantic)
<br>              → Line break
<hr>              → Horizontal rule (line)

 3. Link & Image
<a href="URL">Link</a>         → Hyperlink
<img src="path" alt="desc">   → Image tag

 4. Tables
<table>           → Table container
<tr>              → Table row
<th>              → Table header cell
<td>              → Table data cell


